   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0059"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII. Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0060"/><supplied type="image-description"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb167626">K. H. Müller</rs>: Landschaft mit
                  Kirche</supplied></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0059"/><date when="1908-05-08">8. 5. 08</date>.</dateline></opener><p>Ich danke Dir, <salute>lieber Freund,</salute> u. Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t für Eure Karte aus <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03461-1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb45258">München</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03461-1">Als letzte Station ihrer Reise waren <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Arthur</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173">Olga Schnitzler</rs> zwischen <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1908-05-02" subtype="date-only"/> und <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1908-05-13" subtype="date-only"/> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb45258">München</rs>. Zuvor waren sie in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb465">Riva del
                     Garda</rs> und <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40260">Bozen</rs>.</note> u. wün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che
               Euch für <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173">Eure</rs> Rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chönes Wetter, angenehme
               Eindrücke u. gute Stimmung. Mit vielen Grüßen an Euch <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Beide</rs><lb/>Dein getreuer <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></p></div>
      </body>
